SubjectBy-elections (2) - Whitby-Oshawa - Yellowhead
PrecisOrder directing that WRITS OF ELECTION do issue in order to fill the vacancies in the House of Commons for the electoral districts of Whitby-Oshawa - Yellowhead, with polling to take place on November 17, 2014.
